STEPS REQUIRED TO SETUP:

1. REQUIREMENTS:
  PHP 5.4 with MYSQLi library installed
  MYSQL

2. Go to /modules/database/config and setup your mysql connection details (this is standard Kohana configuration object)
3. Go to /application/boostrap.php and adjust BASEDIR if required (this is standard Kohana configuration variable)
4. Run ./server.php from CLI

* make sure to allow write to /images/ folder (avatars are stored there, this is iportant if you run the server on linux).

And most of all - go to /database/ and setup your Mysql database with the jack_sql script.
